{"tid":1464340,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"快入！唔講乜中計，現場同公安事件第一身外國記者傾完","createTime":"2019-08-13T14:51:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T15:32:26.000Z","uid":295648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"72c43ccc54d519c843a095aea1788171efe7093b","tid":1464340,"uid":295648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:51:17.000Z","msg":"趕住打，可能1999<br />\n中後段我先到場<br />\n發現有3個可疑人喺到唱雙簧<br />\n不段話見到踢人打人既係帶住耳機，叫我地放人<br />\n佢地不停轉換位置，然後相繼認同對方<br />\n<br />\n跟住我見到有外國記者解釋經過<br />\n佢係第一身見到事發經過，有show相比我地睇<br />\n首先佢話個疑似公安一被發現<br />\n已經好多人圍上去想出手<br />\n佢影到一個人攞住棍想打<br />\n上前想保個公安，比人打傷埋<br />\n個個不斷踢，個記者用身去擋都踢<br />\n眼同手都受傷，比人拉返出來先無事<br />\n佢話開頭用棍篤人嗰個一打完就散水<br />\n我問有無見到&rdquo;帶耳機人&rdquo;<br />\n佢話無，但太亂不能肯定"},{"pid":"ed3882da3b35de674a9e7a39568f4767a04f002b","tid":1464340,"uid":295648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:52:16.000Z","msg":"正常示威者就算嬲<br />\n但出手打埋個記者？"},{"pid":"711b5ca6a32ad60f3807ccb9adfe8a26c56b395a","tid":1464340,"uid":295648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:52:49.000Z","msg":"聽日100%比班狗記招放大來講"},{"pid":"542923cae09ca69b55897a136bb6337d30e48c5b","tid":1464340,"uid":295648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:53:22.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"33c2c00c3fd6a0e7cc3f7b07f3754cf97c9ab998","tid":1464340,"uid":295648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:53:40.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"306902f3c3409cc706171f555e091b8056bc38ef","tid":1464340,"uid":260262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:54:17.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5d76ce26506653f3e3b80e330c3d00e4318a753","tid":1464340,"uid":295648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:54:22.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"59517a8b8b965494274dd01b57cc79c350dc8286","tid":1464340,"uid":